text:
My life did not, begin with you...
But i wish my life, should end with you...

One of the best feelings, In the world is knowing that.
Someone is happy because of you.

Sometimes, crying is the only way your eyes speak,
When your mouth can't explain how broken your heart is.

If you love someone, showing them is better than telling them.
If you stop loving someone, telling them is better than showing them.
Finding out who does not follow me back at https://t.co/b94RYvhBGo.

If you love someone, set them free. 
If they come back they’re yours. If they don’t they never were.
The best feeling in the world is being loved back by the person you love.

I said I was fine, but I never said it didn't hurt.
7 retweets 3 likes
Just seeing your smile makes me feel better inside.

Be Strong.
Easy to say, hard to do.

Relationship never dies a natural death.
They murdered by Ego, Attitude and Ignorance.

Love is like the wind, You can't see it.
But you can feel it.

Love is not about,
How much u say, I love you.
But how much you can prove,
that it's true.

Suicide is stupid? You wanna know what is stupid?
Hurting someone so much emotionally.
That they think suicide is the only answer.

Sometimes, it's better to be. ALONE
Nobody can hurt you.

Touch her heart, not her body.
Steal her attention, not her virginity.
Make her smile, don't waste her tears.

The day i will stop loving you.
Is the day when i will close my eyes forever.

When i die, don't come near my body.
Because my hand may hand not be able to wipe your tears anymore.

There is always someone.
Who cares for you without.
Your Knowledge
Only you can make me happy, when i sad.

A promise means, Everything.
But once it is broken, sorry means NOTHING.
